'''開放媒體聯盟'''（'''Alliance for Open Media'''，簡稱'''AOMedia'''）是一個發展開放影像編碼的非營利組織，目標是開發[[買斷式授權|免專利]]的影像編碼格式，作為[[VP9|VP9影像編碼]]的繼任者，取代需要專利的[[HEVC|HEVC影像編碼]]<ref name="AOMPR2015September">{{Cite press release|title = Alliance for Open Media established to deliver next-generation open media formats|date = 1 September 2015|publisher = Alliance for Open Media|url = http://aomedia.org/press-release/alliance-to-deliver-next-generation-open-media-formats/|access-date = 5 September 2015|archive-url = https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20150903232637/http://aomedia.org/press-release/alliance-to-deliver-next-generation-open-media-formats/|archive-date = 2015-09-03|dead-url = yes}}{{Self-published inline|certain = yes|date = September 2015}}</ref><ref name=AOMCNet2015September>{{cite web |title=Tech giants join forces to hasten high-quality online video |publisher=[[CNET|CNET]] |author=Stephen Shankland |url=http://www.cnet.com/news/tech-giants-join-forces-to-hasten-high-quality-online-video/ |date=2015-09-01 |accessdate=2015-09-01 |archive-date=2015-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150901221548/http://www.cnet.com/news/tech-giants-join-forces-to-hasten-high-quality-online-video/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。創立的成員有[[亞馬遜公司|Amazon]]、[[苹果公司|Apple]]、[[思科系统|Cisco]]、[[Facebook|Facebook]]、[[Google|Google]]、[[英特尔|Intel]]、[[微软|微軟]]、[[Mozilla公司|Mozilla]]、[[Netflix|Netflix]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=They Developed It. They Benefit From It. They Stand Behind It.|url=https://aomedia.org/membership/members/|access-date=2022-02-13|work=Alliance for Open Media|language=en}}</ref>。聯盟的目標是在[[BSD授權條款|BSD 2 授權條款]]下發展一個新的影像編碼格式，會從 [[Daala|Daala]]、[[Thor_(视频编码)|Thor]] 和 [[VP10|VP10]] 中取用元素<ref name=AOMMozilla2015September>{{cite news |title=Forging an Alliance for Royalty-Free Video |publisher=[[Mozilla|Mozilla]] |author=David Bryant |url=https://blog.mozilla.org/blog/2015/09/01/forging-an-alliance-for-royalty-free-video/ |date=2015-09-01 |accessdate=2015-09-01 |archive-date=2015-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150902102709/https://blog.mozilla.org/blog/2015/09/01/forging-an-alliance-for-royalty-free-video/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 發展歷史 ==
2015年9月1日，開放媒體聯盟正式宣佈成立，目標是開發免費、免專利的影像編碼格式，來替代需要專利授權的影像編碼 H.264 和 HEVC<ref name=AOMPR2015September/><ref name=AOMCNet2015September/>。目標是在2017年釋出新的影像編碼格式<ref name=AOMCNet2015September/><ref name=AOMStreamingMedia2015September>{{cite news |title=Amazon, Google, and More Working on Royalty-Free Codec |publisher=StreamingMedia.com |author=Jan Ozer |url=http://www.streamingmedia.com/Articles/News/Online-Video-News/Amazon-Google-and-More-Working-on-Royalty-Free-Codec-106091.aspx |date=2015-09-01 |accessdate=2015-09-02 |archive-date=2015-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150904025006/http://www.streamingmedia.com/Articles/News/Online-Video-News/Amazon-Google-and-More-Working-on-Royalty-Free-Codec-106091.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2016年4月5日，[[AMD|AMD]]、[[ARM|ARM]]、[[NVIDIA|NVIDIA]]宣佈加入<ref name=AOMPR2016April>{{cite news |title=The Alliance for Open Media Welcomes New Members and Announces Availability of Open Source Video Codec Project |publisher=Alliance for Open Media |url=http://aomedia.org/press-release/the-alliance-for-open-media-welcomes-new-members-and-announces/ |date=2016-04-05 |accessdate=2016-04-07 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20160420011712/http://aomedia.org/press-release/the-alliance-for-open-media-welcomes-new-members-and-announces/ |archive-date=2016-04-20 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2018年，MPEG創辦人兼主席承認該聯盟是MPEG商業模式的最大威脅，並指出<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://boingboing.net/2018/01/30/rent-seekers-rant.html|title=After industry adopts open video standards, MPEG founder says the end is nigh|last=Doctorow|first=Cory|date=Jan 30, 2018|website=boingboing.net|language=en-US|access-date=March 16, 2018|archive-date=2021-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210507172056/https://boingboing.net/2018/01/30/rent-seekers-rant.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>：
{{quote
|text=開放媒體聯盟（AOM）已經佔據了MPEG過時的影片壓縮技術（[[H.264/MPEG-4_AVC|AVC]]）、具有競爭性的免專利標準（{{link-en|IVC|Internet_Video_Coding}}）的缺席以及無法用於的現代標準的（[[HEVC|HEVC]]）市場所留下的空白...每個人都意識到，MPEG陳舊的商業模式已經破裂。
